Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:36.44,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting interference across all regular comm channels!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.44,0:24:38.97,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's extending across all of lunar orbit! We believe it to be multi-source phase interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.97,0:24:41.17,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So the interference is in the\NNavstar network itself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.17,0:24:41.97,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:45.14,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Has there been any word through the administration company's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.14,0:24:46.64,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Navstar help line about the interference?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.48,0:24:49.22,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're currently trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.22,0:24:50.58,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely being...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.58,0:24:53.69,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Mom, they say I'll be well enough to go on vacation next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.69,0:24:56.62,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all go to the ice crater, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.62,0:24:58.42,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Yahoo!
